headlines.description: — Whether or not Boston catches the Milwaukee Bucks in the Eastern Conference standings, the Celtics will have reason to feel confident if the teams meet in the playoffs for a second straight season.
headlines.shortLinkText: Tatum, Brown help Celtics demolish NBA-leading Bucks 140-99

events.name: New Orleans Pelicans at Denver Nuggets

headlines.description: — Brandon Ingram had 31 points, 11 rebounds and 10 assists for his third triple-double of the season and the New Orleans Pelicans took advantage of Nikola Jokic’s absence to beat the Denver Nuggets 107-88 on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Ingram has triple-double to help Pelicans rout Nuggets
